Protocol Information

Aave is an Open Source and Non-Custodial protocol to earn interest on deposits and borrow assets

Website aave bgd-labs Twitter Safe Harbor Agreement

Methodology

TVL: Total value of all coins held in the smart contracts of the protocol

Fees : Include borrow interest, flashloan fee, liquidation fee and penalty paid by borrowers. View code on GitHub Revenue : Amount of fees go to Aave treasury. View code on GitHub

Holders Revenue :
Aave V2 : View code on GitHub Aave V3 : Aave starts buy back AAVE tokens using Aave Treasury after 9th April 2025. View code on GitHub

Incentives: Tokens allocated to users through liquidity mining or incentive schemes, typically as part of governance or reward mechanisms.

Earnings: Revenue of the protocol minus the incentives distributed to users
